title: Community Economic Development Committee 2/26/21
description:
City Inside/Out looks at programs supporting immigrant essential workers

In-person attendance is currently prohibited per Washington State Governor's Proclamation 20-28.15., until the COVID-19 State of Emergency is terminated or Proclamation 20-28 is rescinded by the Governor or State legislature. Meeting participation is limited to access by telephone conference line and online by the Seattle Channel.

Agenda: Call to Order; Approval of the Agenda; Public Comment; Appointments and Reappointments to Seattle Commission for People with Disabilities, Seattle LGBTQ Commission, Seattle Human Rights Commission, Seattle Women's Commission, Seattle Arts Commission, Equitable Development Initiative Advisory Board; Black Brilliance Research Project - Final Presentation.
